			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4290365">
									

<p>These are well-written letters and I was able to easily slip into the imagery in my head provided by them. My only confusion is maybe some of the language choices uses by the main character? They are a bit high brow for what I would expect, but, this is easily worked around mentally with the idea that everyone viewed the main character migrant scum rather than checking his actual qualifications.</p>
<p>Re: the font, periods are kind of tough to make out but I didn't have any problems with the context clues in finding full stops.</p>

